And unfortunately, I believe that gareon is right on his 4 points.  Bang on in fact.  If we get different (ie substantial and meaningful) responses to those, I'll probably fall out of my chair.
<br />

<br />
So I hope I fall out of my chair!  =)<br />_________________<br />Eriol Telcontar
